some dependecies I used in this project

yarn add react-router bootstrap reactstrap uuid
yarn add react-router-dom

npm install express mongoose
npm install nodemon
yarn add axios OU npm install axios
yarn add cors ou npm install cors

//how to use
yarn run devServer - to init the devServer
connect to mongo compass
and yarn start on client side

